{"tid":1966571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李嘉誠對Zoom的早期投資獲利「翻3倍」","createTime":"2020-04-10T09:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T12:37:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"49b39bd1fe93132aadd35d1a0ee8485c8c7bb46d","tid":1966571,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:25:37.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠對Zoom的早期投資獲利「翻3倍」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4462898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4462898&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi629Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=fbe12456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/4462898</a><br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠早期靠房地產和基礎設施成為香港首富，而在當前的疫情危機中，為李嘉誠帶來回報的卻是一筆科技業投資。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據監管備案，被崇拜者尊稱為「超人」的李嘉誠是 Zoom Video Communications (ZM-US) 的早期投資人，持股 Zoom 大約 8.6%，而 2019 年 4 月 Zoom 在美國上市時，李嘉誠的股份價值約 8.5 億美元，但在今年，這筆股權價值已飆至 29 億美元，這是彭博億萬富豪指數追蹤李嘉誠的公開持股中，今年唯一取得正成長的資產。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據統計，李嘉誠在香港受到抗議示威和肺炎疫情打擊後，李嘉誠的整體財富今年下降了約 50 億美元至 260 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據監管備案，今年 91 歲的李嘉誠通過 3 個投資工具持股 Zoom，根據 Zoom 網站顯示，李嘉誠的維港投資 (Horizons Ventures) 在 2013 年領投了這家視頻會議公司 650 萬美元的 B 輪融資，並參與了兩年後 3000 萬美元的 C 輪融資。<br />\n<br />\n在全球很多地區因肺炎疫情而社交遠離 (Social distancing) 時，Zoom 的視訊會議軟體已成為企業們的重要工具，故引領了 Zoom 股價先前出現一波飆升，不過，由於資訊安全問題，Zoom 股價最近有所回落。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠不是唯一從 Zoom 大漲中受益的人。根據《彭博社》數據顯示，Zoom 創始人袁征目前身家為 61 億美元。原雅虎聯合創始人楊致遠也是早期投資者。監管文件顯示，Zoom 股票暴漲之前，David Bonderman 的家族理財室、Wildcat Capital Management 在去年年底入股。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">李嘉誠的其他一些公司正在幫助擴大 Zoom 的用戶基礎，和記電訊旗下的移動子公司 3 香港在 3 月 18 日的聲明中說，向香港上千家學校捐贈通訊服務組合，其中包括免費的「Zoom 型學堂」。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"47ac1887fca4b5bc2b960bf40015fbfd087f18a8","tid":1966571,"uid":15984,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"其實冇意思<br />\n佢個集團一年投資幾十間初創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本上年年佢都搵到啲獨角獸"},{"pid":"1e40e60ea1ffd7d89c6091271d80f21b72be8fe8","tid":1966571,"uid":259980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ce5a097d51d3226cdd9b6ffb475ceffc6a209f","tid":1966571,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"要甩手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6235292b470e5dc23ec53dfee2ae320ebf3eb84","tid":1966571,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"可惜zoom係based in China"},{"pid":"d99a95d1a36bb81c2b868338974e7da10cf24a1a","tid":1966571,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6235292b470e5dc23ec53dfee2ae320ebf3eb84","tid":1966571,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"可惜zoom係based in China"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"San Jose based"},{"pid":"002511fd2521bf2ec888ccbef96559e50d873dc8","tid":1966571,"uid":92467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d99a95d1a36bb81c2b868338974e7da10cf24a1a","tid":1966571,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6235292b470e5dc23ec53dfee2ae320ebf3eb84","tid":1966571,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:29:39.000Z","msg":"可惜zoom係based in China"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"San Jose based"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"Data based in China<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14f42e888fa7591ecc7e323f4a9e1f6f21e01c9","tid":1966571,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislik